OL,3,CThe end of brewing in Wolverhampton as
OL,4,CCarlsberg brewery set to close
OL,6,FBeer will no longer be brewed in
OL,7,FWolverhampton after Carlsberg
OL,8,FMarston's Brewing Company (CMBC)
OL,9,Frevealed plans to close the site.
OL,11,FBanks's Brewery will shut in Autumn
OL,12,F2025, as part of a restructuring of
OL,13,FCMBC's brewery network.
OL,15,FThe proposed restructuring comes in
OL,16,Fresponse to the decision by Mahou San
OL,17,FMiguel not to renew its long-term
OL,18,Fexclusive licence partnership from
OL,19,F2025 and the decline of cask ale
OL,20,Fvolumes over several years.
