OL,3,CThe end of brewing in Wolverhampton as
OL,4,CCarlsberg brewery set to close
OL,6,FCMBC says it will be supporting
OL,7,Fcolleagues impacted by these
OL,8,Fproposals, including the 97 people
OL,9,Femployed at Banks's Brewery.
OL,11,FThe firm added that it will be working
OL,12,Fwith trade union and colleague
OL,13,Frepresentatives throughout the
OL,14,Fconsultation process.
OL,16,FAs part of the network restructuring,
OL,17,FCMBC will increase investment in its
OL,18,Fbreweries in Northampton and Burton-
OL,19,Fupon-Trent.
