OL,3,CThe end of brewing in Wolverhampton as
OL,4,CCarlsberg brewery set to close
OL,6,FThe long-term goal is to establish
OL,7,FMarston's Brewery in Burton as a
OL,8,Fnational centre for craft beer and
OL,9,Ftraditional ale brewing in the UK,
OL,10,Fwith #6million to be invested in new
OL,11,Fprojects.
OL,13,FThese include the refurbishment of the
OL,14,Fsite's cask ale line to brew
OL,15,Ftraditional British ales, as well
OL,16,Fdeveloping the brewery's capabilities
OL,17,Ffor brewing innovative, contemporary
OL,18,Fcraft ales.
