OL,3,CThe end of brewing in Wolverhampton as
OL,4,CCarlsberg brewery set to close
OL,6,FCMBC will also be investing in a new
OL,7,Flogistics depot in the Black Country
OL,8,Fregion to support its nationwide
OL,9,Fsecondary logistics network.
OL,11,FPaul Davies, CEO of CMBC, said: "This
OL,12,Fhas been an extremely difficult
OL,13,Fdecision, however it has been
OL,14,Fnecessary to restructure our business
OL,15,Fto maintain our competitiveness in a
OL,16,Fchallenging UK beer market.
