OL,6,F"The hard reality is that, because of
OL,7,Fthe current climate for ale and Mahou
OL,8,FSan Miguel's decision not to renew its
OL,9,Fexclusive production and distribution
OL,10,Fagreement with CMBC from the start of
OL,11,Fnext year, we will have significant
OL,12,Fexcess capacity across our brewery
OL,13,Fnetwork which we have to address.
OL,15,F"The team at Banks's has been
OL,16,Funwavering in its dedication and
OL,17,Fcommitment to the brewery. We will
OL,18,Fensure that we support all our people
OL,19,Fclosely throughout this extremely
OL,20,Fchallenging period.
